[32m│[0m - Error: "Sorry you can't use: '<'"                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Reason: Contains `<` character                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Payload 4: `"><img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>`**                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Status: BLOCKED                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Error: "Sorry you can't use: '<'"                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Reason: Contains `<` character                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Key Findings:**                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The filter blocks payloads **before reflection** - it detects dangerous    [32m│[0m
